1	Organizational Strategic Alignment v1	\N	Welcome to the Organizational Strategic Alignment assessment. 	The Organizational Strategic Alignment™ (OSA) assessment measures your organization's capability to execute its strategy. Specifically, it measures your organization’s deep drivers (similar to an individual’s DNA) which determine its culture and guides it performance.\n<br><br>\nThe results provide management and you with a snapshot of the underlying structure and dynamics of your organization.\n<br><br>\nThe questionnaire consists of 63 questions and 7 demographic questions. Most people complete the entire questionnaire in 10 minutes. Please answer the questions from your own perspective and experience. \n<br><br>\nAll individual results are kept completely anonymous and confidential and will never be shared on an individual basis.\n<br><br>\nThank you,\n<br><br>\nStrategia Analytics Team\n	Thank you for responding to this assessment.	We appreciate your responses and your insights. If you have any questions about the assessment, please contact Strategia Analytics at <a href="http://www.strategiaanalytics.com">www.strategiaanalytics.com</a>.\n<br><br>\nThe Strategia Analytics Team	0	\N	0	en
